Test fixtures for oven-vision pipeline stages.

Place real oven images here for meaningful benchmarks and stage testing.

Expected files:
  oven.jpg     - Full 2560x1440 frame from go2rtc (used by criterion benches
                 and the stage runner when --input is not specified).

If no real images are present, the benchmark and runner tools generate
synthetic grey frames. These are useful for profiling call overhead and
verifying stages compile, but do not exercise real CV logic.
